As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 880 people, 522 households, and 284 families residing in the town.

===2010 census===
As of the [[census]]<ref name="GR2" /> of 2010, there were 900 people in Oriental and 13,074 in Pamlico County. Oriental had 477 households in the last census.

